      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, though upon close inspection, you will find some typical minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few faint swirl marks in the clear coat. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather seats are well-preserved with only light creasing on the driver's side bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a solid service history, though it will likely need a new set of tires within the next 5,000 miles. It is a reliable, honest car that is ready for its next owner.",
