    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolutely wonderful to me. It's in great shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for your daily commute or a fun weekend road trip! I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner. Come take it for a spin, you'll love how it drives!",
