    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels via a Variable M Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS unit refresh and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis integrity. The engine pulls strongly across the entire power band with no rod bearing noise, and the suspension geometry remains true. A mechanically robust driver\u2019s car for the purist seeking analog feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
