      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, which exemplifies a harmonious balance of performance and preservation. Demonstrating consistent mechanical upkeep and a well-appointed interior, this motorcar offers a sophisticated driving experience for the discerning professional. Its condition reflects a history of diligent care, ensuring both reliability and a commanding presence on the road. This is a premier opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that meets rigorous standards of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
