    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It's been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and consistently maintained, so it\u2019s totally ready for all your upcoming adventures. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out for a fun weekend getaway, this beauty is ready to hit the road. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 31500.0,
