      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8, renowned for its 8,250 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is paired with a longitudinal 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock, providing an unfiltered mechanical connection to the tarmac. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), maintaining excellent damping rates for both high-velocity cornering and daily compliance. This vehicle has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the structural and mechanical integrity of the high-revving valvetrain. A compelling choice for the purist seeking a visceral, analog performance profile.",
